android.car

类 VehicleAreaSeat

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.VehicleAreaSeat

  • public final class VehicleAreaSeat
extends java.lang.Object
    Object used to indicate the area value for car properties which have area type VehicleAreaType.VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_SEAT.

    The constants defined by VehicleAreaSeat indicate the position for area type VehicleAreaType.VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_SEAT. A property can have a single or a combination of positions. Developers can query the position using CarPropertyManager.getAreaId(int, int).

    Refer to CarPropertyConfig.getAreaIds() for more information about areaId.
